dmca.title: Client Complains to Graphic Designer
dmca.body:
Larry,

This is Shannon from 160over90.  Please cease and desist immediately from making any reference to doing work for 160over90 or any of its past clients.  You are contractually not permitted to use our logo or our work as anything that you did for 160over90 was work-for-hire.  Furthermore it is causing confusion in the marketplace and jeopardizing our business.  Please confirm your intent to remove our logo and reference to that work immediately as well as any logos or reference to work for any of 160over90
